Package: separableNNT
Type: Package
Title: NNT for Survival Endpoints based on Separable Effects
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2023-04-23
Author: Zhao Yang, Yue Qim Jiayi Sun, Jun Lium Miao Wang, Qiujv Deng, Yongchen Hao, Na Yang, Zhili Ji, Xiao-Hua Zhou, Jing Liu
Maintainer: Zhao Yang <yangz98@connect.hku.hk>
Description: Reproduce the proposed method in Yang et al.'s paper (2023) <doi:>, in which the Number Needed to Treat (NNT) for survival endpoint proposed by Yang and Yin's paper (2019) <doi:10.1371/journal.pone.0223301> is calculated using separable effects in the presence of competing events proposed by Stensrud et al (2022) <doi:https://doi.org/10.1080/01621459.2020.1765783>. 
Depends: R (>= 3.2.0)
Imports: parallel, survival, stats
Suggests: rmarkdown, knitr, ggplot2, ggsci, foreign, Hmisc
License: GPL (>=2)
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
VignetteBuilder: knitr
